# PATCH 006: Antigravity anti-fingerprinting on top of upstream version updates
#
# Keeps the fork-specific Antigravity fingerprinting behavior that upstream still
# lacks:
# - deterministic per-account platform fingerprints without version downgrade
# - structured session IDs salted by auth/model/project
# - broader random project-name pools
# - targeted tests for the fingerprint helpers
